		</p>
		<SocialList />
	</section>
	<section class="mt-10">
		<h2 class="title mb-4 text-xl">Professional experience</h2>
		<div class="space-y-6 pl-2">
			<div>
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between">
					<h3 class="text-base">Software Engineer: BigBinary</h3>
					<h3 class="text-base">Aug 2022 - Present</h3>
				</div>
				<ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
					<li>
						Contributed to the development of
						<a href="https://www.neeto.com/" target="_blank"><span class="underline">neeto</span></a
						>
						apps utilizing Rails and React.
					</li>
					<li>
						Developed npm packages, Ruby gems, and Chrome extensions as part of ongoing projects.
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div>
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between pl-2">
					<h3 class="text-base">Software Engineer Intern: Fynarfin</h3>
